ActCombating Counterfeit Products Act
Economic Action Plan 2015 Act, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing November 5, 2018 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the two Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) November 5, 2018 as the day on which subsection 50(3) of the COMBATING COUNTERFEIT PRODUCTS ACT, chapter 32 of the Statutes of Canada, 2014, COMES INTO FORCE; and, (2) November 5, 2018 as the day on which sections 63 and 68 of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2015, NO.1, chapter 36, COME INTO FORCE.
